Steps to install SASS:

1. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using NVM (Linux):
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   $ exit
   # Reopened terminal
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16

2. Verified Node.js installation:
   $ node -v

3. Installed Sass version 3.7.4 globally:
   $ npm install -g sass@3.7.4

4. Verified Sass installation:
   $ sass --version
# npm install sass -v 3.7.4